'''Team Ozone Xenon''' is a second/third amateur team sponsored by Ozone Gear in Taiwan, formed in May, 2013. Ozone Gaming also created another team which called [[Team Ozone Blade]] at the same time. In 2014, Ozone is no longer the sponsor of eMD and team name changes to '''eXtreme Divide e-Sport Team'''.

